WEBVTT

00:01.902 --> 00:03.737
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON THE "HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

00:03.737 --> 00:06.239
JEFFERY HARRINGTON
WAS ARRESTED. D.U.I.

00:06.239 --> 00:07.774
THREE CELLS IN A ROW.

00:07.774 --> 00:10.043
PUT THEM TOGETHER
AND JEFFERY IN THE MIDDLE.

00:10.043 --> 00:12.112
‐AND ALL THIS YOU.
‐PAY YOU FOR ONE.

00:12.112 --> 00:13.479
HOW MUCH WAS YOUR HOUSE
AND HERS?

00:13.479 --> 00:15.081
‐COUPLE MILLION.
‐CHECK OUT THAT LINK.

00:15.081 --> 00:16.650
‐WOW.
‐JUICY, HUH?

00:16.650 --> 00:18.118
FIND THIS NEWSPAPER

00:18.118 --> 00:19.786
AND MAKE SURE
TO GET A COPY OF IT.

00:19.786 --> 00:20.887
WHAT'S THAT?

00:20.887 --> 00:22.288
VERONICA,
ARE YOU HAVING AN AFFAIR?

00:22.288 --> 00:23.924
‐W‐WHAT?
‐READ IT.

00:23.924 --> 00:26.326
YOU PLAYED ME
FOR A DAMN FOOL.

00:26.326 --> 00:27.427
YOU!

00:41.441 --> 00:43.409
YOU DO THAT?

00:43.409 --> 00:45.278
YES.

00:45.278 --> 00:46.747
BY YOURSELF?

00:46.747 --> 00:48.649
YEAH.

00:48.649 --> 00:51.384
GOOD WORK.

00:51.384 --> 00:52.452
THANKS.

00:54.487 --> 00:56.256
LOOK AT YOU.

00:56.256 --> 00:58.058
GET UP.

01:08.341 --> 01:10.611
I'M SORRY, CANDY.

01:10.611 --> 01:12.212
BUT YOU KNOW ME.

01:12.212 --> 01:14.848
I DO.

01:14.848 --> 01:16.617
YOU KNOW I'M HURT, RIGHT?

01:16.617 --> 01:18.484
YEAH, I KNOW.

01:18.484 --> 01:20.386
WHY YOU LIE TO ME,
CANDY?

01:22.422 --> 01:23.389
I'M SORRY.

01:23.389 --> 01:25.826
NO.
DON'T DO THAT.

01:25.826 --> 01:27.694
THAT'S THE SAME STUFF
MY MOM USED TO PULL

01:27.694 --> 01:29.395
AFTER SHE WOULD DROP
HOT BAKING SODA ON ME

01:29.395 --> 01:30.797
FROM HER PIPE IN MY BED.

01:30.797 --> 01:31.832
I AM...

01:31.832 --> 01:33.600
WHAT?

01:36.870 --> 01:38.471
I SHOULD HAVE TOLD YOU.

01:38.471 --> 01:39.773
WHY DIDN'T YOU?

01:39.773 --> 01:42.008
I‐I JUST ‐‐

01:42.008 --> 01:45.045
NO, YOU THOUGHT
YOU COULD GET AWAY WITH IT

01:45.045 --> 01:48.414
AND I WOULDN'T FIND OUT.

01:48.414 --> 01:50.751
‐NO, I DIDN'T.
‐YES, YOU DID.

01:50.751 --> 01:53.153
‐I THOUGHT ‐‐
‐NO. NO.

01:53.153 --> 01:55.388
YOU WEREN'T THINKING.

01:55.388 --> 01:57.090
‐I WASN'T.
‐NO.

01:57.090 --> 02:03.103
YOU KNOW...I DON'T
GIVE A DAMN ABOUT NOBODY.

02:03.103 --> 02:06.673
BUT YOU ‐‐

02:06.673 --> 02:09.976
YOU WERE MY GIRL.

02:09.976 --> 02:12.879
YOUR MOM USED
TO LOOK AFTER ME,

02:12.879 --> 02:17.283
GIVE ME FOOD
AND CLOTHES.

02:20.053 --> 02:23.690
I WAS HOLDING YOU DOWN.

02:23.690 --> 02:25.425
I KNOW AND ‐‐

02:25.425 --> 02:27.761
DON'T YOU DO THAT.

02:27.761 --> 02:30.831
DON'T SAY YOU'RE SORRY.

02:30.831 --> 02:32.633
OKAY.

02:35.368 --> 02:38.672
YOU OWE ME MONEY.

02:38.672 --> 02:41.474
I DON'T HAVE ‐‐
I DON'T HAVE IT.

02:45.846 --> 02:47.881
[ SIGHS ]

02:47.881 --> 02:49.215
CANDY, DO YOU WANT
TO GO WITH Q?

02:49.215 --> 02:51.317
NO.

02:51.317 --> 02:54.855
PLEASE, WAR.
NO.

02:54.855 --> 02:57.257
THEN GIVE ME THE MONEY.

03:01.067 --> 03:03.737
WAR, I DON'T HAVE IT.

03:03.737 --> 03:05.138
YOU DON'T HAVE IT?

03:05.138 --> 03:07.708
‐NO.
‐OH.

03:10.611 --> 03:13.013
THIS IS A NICE PLACE.

03:13.013 --> 03:16.249
IT'S YOURS.
YOU ‐‐ YOU CAN HAVE IT.

03:18.318 --> 03:21.688
YOU THINK
I WANT TO LIVE HERE?

03:21.688 --> 03:24.558
WITH ALL THESE PEOPLE LOOKING
AT ME EVERY FIVE MINUTES,

03:24.558 --> 03:26.527
WATCHING MY BUSINESS?

03:26.527 --> 03:29.696
NO, THANK YOU.

03:29.696 --> 03:32.799
I WANT THE MONEY.
JUST GET ME THE MONEY.

03:32.799 --> 03:35.936
COME ON, BABY.
JUST GIVE ME ‐‐

03:35.936 --> 03:37.170
WAR, I DON'T ‐‐

03:37.170 --> 03:40.240
JUST GIVE ME THE MONEY.

03:40.240 --> 03:42.709
I DON'T HAVE IT.

03:42.709 --> 03:44.110
DAMN. DAMN.

03:44.110 --> 03:47.548
DAMN. DAMN.

03:47.548 --> 03:49.049
THEN I GOT TO KILL YOU.

03:49.049 --> 03:51.284
WAR, NO.

03:53.754 --> 03:55.188
I WANT YOU TO BE STILL.

03:55.188 --> 03:56.923
WAR.

03:56.923 --> 03:59.292
DON'T MOVE.
SHH.

03:59.292 --> 04:00.767
SIT DOWN.

04:00.767 --> 04:03.069
THAT'S A GOOD GIRL.

04:03.069 --> 04:05.405
YOU WON'T EVEN
FEEL IT, I PROMISE.

04:05.405 --> 04:06.372
WAR.

04:06.372 --> 04:09.309
SHH.

04:09.309 --> 04:12.245
I'M GONNA MAKE THIS
QUICK.

04:12.245 --> 04:14.915
PLEASE DON'T.

04:14.915 --> 04:18.885
DON'T MOVE.

04:21.154 --> 04:22.422
[ GUNSHOT ]

