29:29.630 --> 29:31.532
I'M SORRY, VERONICA.

29:31.532 --> 29:34.668
I'M SO SORRY THAT I TRIED
TO CHOKE THE LIFE OUT OF YOU.

29:34.668 --> 29:37.337
I'M SORRY
THAT I GOT MY HANDS

29:37.337 --> 29:41.041
WRAPPED AROUND THAT ADAM'S APPLE
OF YOURS SO LONG AGO.

29:41.041 --> 29:42.776
IT SHOULD HAVE BEEN SOONER.

29:42.776 --> 29:44.444
I'M REALLY SORRY.

29:46.847 --> 29:48.782
AND YOU'RE STILL NOT
GONNA DEFEND ME?

29:48.782 --> 29:50.717
'CAUSE I TOLD YOU
TO STOP IT

29:50.717 --> 29:53.486
AND YOU REFUSED
TO LISTEN. YOU CONTINUE ‐‐

29:53.486 --> 29:57.023
THAT'S BECAUSE I'M WAITING
FOR YOU TO DO SOMETHING, MAN!

29:57.023 --> 29:58.892
DO SOMETHING!

29:58.892 --> 30:00.226
STOP BEING HIS FLUNKY.

30:00.226 --> 30:02.468
YOU'RE NOT HIS ERRAND BOY.
STOP IT!

30:02.468 --> 30:04.270
DAVID...

30:19.285 --> 30:22.422
THERE YOU GO ‐‐
ONE BIG FAMILY REUNION.

30:29.763 --> 30:31.131
Veronica: JEFFERY?

30:35.969 --> 30:37.771
MOM?

30:37.771 --> 30:39.372
SON.

30:39.372 --> 30:41.908
DAD?

30:41.908 --> 30:43.143
WHAT ARE YOU GUYS DOING HERE?

30:43.143 --> 30:46.046
WHY ARE YOU HERE?

30:46.046 --> 30:47.648
DID SHE HAVE YOU ARRESTED?

30:47.648 --> 30:49.249
‐WHO?
‐THE D. A.

30:49.249 --> 30:51.051
UH, NO.

30:51.051 --> 30:53.419
THEN WHY ARE YOU HERE?
WHAT'S GOING ON?

30:53.419 --> 30:56.890
I, UH...

30:56.890 --> 30:59.392
JEFFERY?

30:59.392 --> 31:02.468
JEFFERY.
‐SPEAK, SON.

31:04.204 --> 31:05.238
I GOT ARRESTED.

31:05.238 --> 31:06.907
WELL, I CAN SEE THAT.

31:06.907 --> 31:09.776
WHAT WAS THE CHARGE?

31:09.776 --> 31:11.311
DUI.

31:11.311 --> 31:14.014
‐OH, JEFFERY.
‐HAVE YOU LOST YOUR MIND?

31:16.783 --> 31:18.985
WAIT A MINUTE.
WHY ARE YOU HERE, MOM?

31:24.858 --> 31:27.093
RIGHT.

31:27.093 --> 31:30.296
AT LEAST FOR ME,
I HAVE BEEN FALSELY ACCUSED.

31:30.296 --> 31:32.132
YEAH. RIGHT.

31:34.300 --> 31:36.069
DRINKING AND DRIVING.

31:36.069 --> 31:38.204
LYING...

31:38.204 --> 31:39.372
MANIPULATING...

31:39.372 --> 31:42.442
ALL RIGHT, SON, ENOUGH.

31:42.442 --> 31:45.879
WE ARE TALKING GUILTY.

31:45.879 --> 31:49.816
YOU'RE GETTING
BESIDE YOURSELF.

31:49.816 --> 31:52.586
THE APPLE DOESN'T FALL TOO FAR
FROM THE TREE, MOM.

31:52.586 --> 31:54.988
OH, OKAY.

31:54.988 --> 31:56.557
WELL, I WILL SHOW YOU.

31:56.557 --> 31:59.760
SHUT UP.

31:59.760 --> 32:01.367
YOU HAVE NOTHING ON ME.

32:01.367 --> 32:04.905
JUST SHUT UP.

32:04.905 --> 32:07.508
YOU KNOW,
WHEN I GET OUT OF HERE,

32:07.508 --> 32:10.644
YOU WILL REGRET EVER
TALKING TO ME THAT WAY.

32:14.881 --> 32:17.584
WHEN WE GET OUT OF HERE,

32:17.584 --> 32:21.054
YOU'RE GONNA REGRET EVERYTHING
YOU EVER DID TO ME.

32:25.892 --> 32:28.629
I ALWAYS
HAVE THE UPPER HAND.

32:28.629 --> 32:31.665
REMEMBER THAT.

32:31.665 --> 32:34.835
DO YOU?

32:34.835 --> 32:36.970
WHAT DO YOU HAVE?

32:36.970 --> 32:39.573
HMM?

32:39.573 --> 32:42.042
A DESK...

32:42.042 --> 32:44.811
SCRAPED KNEES...

32:44.811 --> 32:47.247
FROM BEING
ON A RAGGEDY OLD FLOOR

32:47.247 --> 32:50.817
AT A JUNKYARD.

32:50.817 --> 32:54.454
WOW.
WERE THE HELL IS THIS GOING?

32:54.454 --> 32:57.490
DO YOU REALLY WANT
TO GO THERE WITH ME?

32:57.490 --> 32:59.693
SHALL WE?

32:59.693 --> 33:03.036
DO YOU WANT TO TELL DAD
OR SHALL I?

33:03.036 --> 33:05.906
TELL ME WHAT?

33:05.906 --> 33:09.242
NO,
YOU GO RIGHT AHEAD.

33:09.242 --> 33:10.844
DON'T PUSH ME.

33:10.844 --> 33:12.646
GO ON.

33:20.521 --> 33:23.089
I'M HAVING AN AFFAIR
WITH A YOUNG MAN.

33:23.089 --> 33:27.828
APPARENTLY JEFFERY
KNOWS ABOUT IT.

33:27.828 --> 33:30.230
PROBABLY SAW IT
IN THE PAPER.

33:30.230 --> 33:31.397
PAPER?

33:31.397 --> 33:32.799
YES.
IT'S IN THE PAPER.

33:32.799 --> 33:35.235
DID YOU SEE IT?

33:35.235 --> 33:37.904
I'M SURE...

33:37.904 --> 33:40.006
I'M SURE YOUR FATHER HAS.

33:45.078 --> 33:49.282
SO, GO ON.
MAKE YOUR POWER MOVE...

33:49.282 --> 33:50.651
AND HURT YOUR FATHER.

33:50.651 --> 33:53.887
YOU HURT HIM.
YOU HURT HIM.

33:53.887 --> 33:56.356
YOU'RE NOT GONNA
TURN THIS AROUND ON ME.

33:56.356 --> 33:58.091
I DIDN'T DO ANYTHING TO HIM.
YOU DID.

33:58.091 --> 34:01.735
OH, YOU JUST WANT TO DO WYATT
AND ANY OTHER MAN.

34:01.735 --> 34:05.305
YES, I DO.

34:05.305 --> 34:08.274
AND I WISH THERE WAS ONE
IN HERE RIGHT NOW.

34:08.274 --> 34:10.376
I WOULD DO IT
IN YOUR FACE

34:10.376 --> 34:12.378
AND FORCE YOU TO WATCH IT.

34:21.855 --> 34:24.725
OKAY, JEFFERY.

34:24.725 --> 34:26.527
WELL, I'VE TRIED
TO BE NICE.

34:30.396 --> 34:33.099
SON...

34:33.099 --> 34:36.603
WHO IS THAT
IN THE PICTURE?

34:36.603 --> 34:39.706
DO YOU KNOW WHO THAT IS?

34:39.706 --> 34:41.508
JEFFERY...

34:45.879 --> 34:47.413
NO. I DON'T.

34:49.482 --> 34:51.117
I THINK YOU DO.

34:51.117 --> 34:52.786
I SAID I DON'T.

34:52.786 --> 34:54.588
ARE YOU SURE?

35:02.035 --> 35:04.838
WHEN I GET OUT OF HERE...

35:04.838 --> 35:08.909
I THINK I WILL SLEEP
WITH MAGGIE DAY AFTER ALL.

35:08.909 --> 35:11.077
AND THAT WILL MAKE US EVEN.

35:11.077 --> 35:13.213
NO, IT WON'T.

35:13.213 --> 35:16.482
BUT IT WILL MAKE US OVER.

35:16.482 --> 35:19.485
UM, DAVID, YOU STILL WANT ME
TO CALL IT OFF?

35:20.120 --> 35:23.056
ASS.

35:23.056 --> 35:26.226
JEFFERY.

35:26.226 --> 35:27.994
JEFF.

35:27.994 --> 35:30.597
JEFFERY, COME CLOSE.

35:30.597 --> 35:32.265
DON'T COUNT ON IT.

35:32.265 --> 35:33.934
WOW.

35:33.934 --> 35:36.069
LOOK WHO'S FINALLY
GROWING UP.

35:36.069 --> 35:37.838
UNLIKE WYATT.

35:45.646 --> 35:48.381
JEFFERY...

35:48.381 --> 35:49.750
LET ME ASK YOU A QUESTION.

35:49.750 --> 35:53.153
ARE YOU ‐‐
ARE YOU STILL GAY?

35:53.153 --> 35:54.688
‐JIM.
‐NO, NO, NO.

35:54.688 --> 35:57.357
YOU SEE, JEFFERY, YOUR FATHER
AND I ARE BOTH DELIGHTED

35:57.357 --> 35:58.659
THAT YOU'VE COME
OUT OF THE CLOSET.

35:58.659 --> 36:00.527
I KNOW HE'S GAY.
YOU KNOW HE'S GAY.

36:00.527 --> 36:03.303
EVERYONE KNOWS YOU ARE GAY
EXCEPT YOUR MOTHER.

36:03.303 --> 36:06.607
SHE'S IN DENIAL.
ADMIT IT, VERONICA.

36:06.607 --> 36:09.342
HE IS GAY.

36:09.342 --> 36:11.512
YOU CAN'T CONTROL HIM
OUT OF IT.

36:11.512 --> 36:13.413
IT DOESN'T WORK THAT WAY.

36:13.413 --> 36:16.683
I KNOW THAT.
YOU'RE ‐‐

36:16.683 --> 36:17.984
LET'S SEE WHAT HAPPENS

36:17.984 --> 36:22.288
WHEN YOU DON'T TRY
TO CONTROL YOUR CHILDREN.

36:22.288 --> 36:24.190
THEY TAKE THEIR LIVES
INTO THEIR OWN HANDS,

36:24.190 --> 36:26.993
OR THEY TAKE A PISTOL

36:26.993 --> 36:28.529
AND END THEIR LIFE.

36:28.529 --> 36:31.598
BITCH. I WILL ‐‐
GET ‐‐ NO, NO!

36:31.598 --> 36:33.600
DO YOU SEE, DAVID?
DO YOU SEE WHAT SHE'S DOING?

36:33.600 --> 36:36.069
‐THAT IS STILL MY WIFE.
‐YOU'RE PROTECTING HER.

36:36.069 --> 36:37.838
THAT IS YOUR WIFE
WHO HAS CHEATED ON YOU,

36:37.838 --> 36:39.339
WHO HAS HAD MY SON
RAPED IN PRISON,

36:39.339 --> 36:40.574
AND GOD KNOWS WHAT ELSE.

36:40.574 --> 36:42.543
WHAT?
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

36:42.543 --> 36:44.144
DO YOU NOT SEE IT?

36:44.144 --> 36:46.479
SHE ADMITTED IT RIGHT THERE.

36:46.479 --> 36:48.549
I HAD MY SON
PUT IN PRISON, YES.

36:48.549 --> 36:49.883
BUT I HAD HIM PROTECTED.

36:49.883 --> 36:54.120
AND YOU LET THAT SON OF A BITCH
IN THE CELL WITH MY SON.

36:54.120 --> 36:55.589
YOU DID THAT.

36:55.589 --> 36:57.490
SO YOU WAIT, VERONICA.

36:57.490 --> 37:02.101
YOU JUST WAIT.
IT'S YOUR TURN NEXT.

37:02.101 --> 37:03.870
YOU DID IT?

37:07.140 --> 37:09.108
YOU DID IT?

37:09.108 --> 37:11.745
YOU DID IT.

37:11.745 --> 37:13.647
JUST LIKE YOU LET QUINCY
OUT OF JAIL.

37:13.647 --> 37:15.649
YOU...

37:15.649 --> 37:18.017
YOU GOT HIM OUT OF JAIL.

37:18.017 --> 37:19.720
YEAH, SHE ‐‐
SHE SAID SHE GOT HIM OUT.

37:19.720 --> 37:21.522
Y‐YOU TOLD ME THAT
ON THE PHONE.

37:21.522 --> 37:23.557
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

37:23.557 --> 37:28.194
WHAT?
YOU DID THAT, TOO?

37:28.194 --> 37:29.996
OKAY.
‐MM.

37:34.100 --> 37:36.737
LOOK AT YOU.

37:36.737 --> 37:40.040
HOW COULD YOU DO THAT
TO HIM?

37:40.040 --> 37:42.543
YOU ARE SICK.

37:42.543 --> 37:46.146
SICK.

37:46.146 --> 37:50.016
YOU'RE STILL
IN LOVE WITH HIM?

37:50.016 --> 37:52.452
AFTER ALL...

37:52.452 --> 37:56.122
YOU ARE STILL IN LOVE
WITH HIM?

37:58.058 --> 37:59.960
I'M GONNA DO EVERYTHING
I CAN TO MAKE SURE

37:59.960 --> 38:03.036
YOU NEVER GET OUT OF HERE.

38:03.036 --> 38:05.706
NEVER.

38:05.706 --> 38:09.242
YOU ARE AN EVIL SOUL.

38:09.242 --> 38:13.714
AND YOU DON'T DESERVE TO SEE
THE LIGHT OF DAY...

38:13.714 --> 38:35.936
EVER.

39:00.701 --> 39:03.436
[ KNOCKING ON DOOR ]

39:03.436 --> 39:05.506
CANDY, OPEN UP.
IT'S ME.

39:14.347 --> 39:16.783
‐HEY.
‐HEY.

39:16.783 --> 39:18.785
‐WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?
‐WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?

39:18.785 --> 39:21.655
‐NOTHING.
‐SOMETHING'S WRONG WITH YOU.

39:21.655 --> 39:24.290
WHAT IS IT?
‐NOTHING. NOT FEELING WELL.

39:24.290 --> 39:26.126
TIRED.
WANT TO GO LIE DOWN.

39:26.126 --> 39:29.129
ALL RIGHT, WELL, UH...
CAN I COME INSIDE?

39:29.129 --> 39:30.997
NO.
NOT A GOOD IDEA, BENNY.

39:30.997 --> 39:32.365
CANDACE, I WANT
TO TALK TO YOU.

39:32.365 --> 39:34.200
‐NOT TODAY.
‐CANDACE.

39:34.200 --> 39:36.269
L‐LET'S JUST TALK
RIGHT OUT HERE.

39:36.269 --> 39:38.839
I NEED SOME AIR ANYWAY.
‐OKAY.

39:42.008 --> 39:43.276
WHAT ‐‐ WHAT'S UP?

39:43.276 --> 39:46.580
Y‐YOU KNOW MOM IS MAD
AS HELL RIGHT NOW, RIGHT?

39:46.580 --> 39:49.049
‐WHAT ELSE IS NEW?
‐WELL, SHE'S MAD AT ME.

39:49.049 --> 39:51.351
THAT'S WHAT'S NEW.
‐THAT IS TRUE.

39:51.351 --> 39:52.586
SHE'S NEVER MAD AT YOU.

39:52.586 --> 39:55.889
WELL, UNLESS I'M DOING
SOMETHING WITH YOU.

39:55.889 --> 39:58.258
BENNY, I'M NOT DOING THIS.

39:58.258 --> 40:01.835
I'M TIRED.

40:01.835 --> 40:04.470
WHAT DOES SHE
KEEP STARING AT?

40:04.470 --> 40:06.472
SHE'S JUST NOSY.

40:06.472 --> 40:08.374
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

40:08.374 --> 40:11.612
Y‐YOU KNOW MOM'S STAYING
IN A HOTEL?

40:11.612 --> 40:12.779
OKAY.

40:12.779 --> 40:14.781
AND SHE WON'T COME
TO MY HOUSE.

40:14.781 --> 40:16.049
‐I KNEW THAT.
‐ALL RIGHT.

40:16.049 --> 40:18.284
WELL, WE CAN'T LEAVE HER
IN THIS FLEABAG HOTEL.

40:18.284 --> 40:19.820
WE'RE NOT DOING THAT,
ALL RIGHT?

40:19.820 --> 40:22.288
THE HOUSE IS GONE AND SHE NEEDS
TO COME TO MY HOUSE.

40:22.288 --> 40:25.258
SHE WON'T DO IT.
‐I TOLD YOU.

40:25.258 --> 40:27.861
UNLESS YOU CAN TELL ME HOW YOU
GOT THE MONEY FOR THIS PLACE.

40:27.861 --> 40:29.195
BENNY...

40:29.195 --> 40:30.196
CANDACE, WE'RE NOT GONNA
LEAVE HER OVER THERE, ALL RIGHT?

40:30.196 --> 40:31.998
SO HELP ME OUT HERE.

40:31.998 --> 40:34.968
GIVE ME SOMETHING
TO BRING TO HER.

40:34.968 --> 40:36.670
‐I DON'T CARE.
‐CANDACE,

40:36.670 --> 40:38.038
HOW DID YOU GET THE MONEY
FOR THIS PLACE

40:38.038 --> 40:39.606
AND ALL THIS STUFF?

40:39.606 --> 40:42.208
BENNY, I'M NOT ‐‐
I'M NOT DOING THIS.

40:42.208 --> 40:43.309
I'M TIRED.

40:43.309 --> 40:45.245
WELL...
YOU'RE TIRED.

40:45.245 --> 40:47.681
W‐WHAT IS WRONG WITH YOU?
‐I'M TIRED.

40:47.681 --> 40:48.949
LOOK, I'M NOT TALKING
ABOUT THAT, ALL RIGHT?

40:48.949 --> 40:50.450
YOU USED
TO TELL ME THE TRUTH.

40:50.450 --> 40:53.419
NOW YOU'RE RUNNING AROUND
LYING TO ME ABOUT EVERYTHING.

40:53.419 --> 40:55.088
CANDACE, THIS IS ME HERE.
‐IT'S COMPLICATED.

40:55.088 --> 40:56.122
ALL RIGHT, DON'T TELL ME THAT.
ALL RIGHT?

40:56.122 --> 40:57.791
LET ME BE
THE JUDGE OF THAT.

40:57.791 --> 40:59.292
HOW DID YOU GET
THIS PLACE?!

41:01.535 --> 41:04.204
‐I GOT TO GO.
‐CAND‐‐

41:04.204 --> 41:05.706
‐WELL, I'M COMING INSIDE.
‐NO, YOU'RE NOT.

41:05.706 --> 41:06.840
‐YES, I AM.
‐NO.

41:06.840 --> 41:07.974
‐OPEN THE DOOR, CANDACE.
‐NO.

41:07.974 --> 41:09.042
CANDACE,
GET OUT OF MY WAY.

41:09.042 --> 41:10.043
YOU'RE 100 POUNDS.
COME ON, CANDACE.

41:10.043 --> 41:11.311
‐NO, BENNY.
‐NO, STOP.

41:11.311 --> 41:13.246
BENNY, THAT LADY'S
GONNA CALL THE COPS.

41:13.246 --> 41:14.380
I DON'T CARE
ABOUT THIS WOMAN.

41:14.380 --> 41:15.582
WHAT IF SHE SEES YOU
DOING THIS?

41:15.582 --> 41:17.117
‐NO, I DON'T CARE.
‐CAN'T YOU JUST COME BACK?

41:17.117 --> 41:18.519
NO, I'M NOT.
I WANT TO TALK ABOUT THIS.

41:20.721 --> 41:24.357
WHAT THE HELL, CANDACE?

41:24.357 --> 41:25.391
WHA‐‐

41:27.861 --> 41:31.131
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:31.131 --> 41:32.933
THERE'S TOO MUCH RIGHT NOW.
YOU CAN'T HAVE YOUR INHERITANCE.

41:32.933 --> 41:35.001
WE'VE GOT TO FIND JEFFERY.
DID ‐‐ DID HE GO TO THE POLICE?

41:35.001 --> 41:36.870
‐I‐I DON'T KNOW.
‐DON'T KNOW?

41:36.870 --> 41:39.039
Woman: THEY SAY YOU KNOW HOW TO
FIND Q ON THE TRACKING THING.

41:39.039 --> 41:40.541
SEE?
THERE HE IS.

41:40.541 --> 41:41.775
OH, BABY.
YOU ARE BURNING UP.

41:41.775 --> 41:43.209
STOP PLAYING THE VICTIM.

41:43.209 --> 41:47.347
YOU ARE AN ACTIVE PARTICIPANT
IN EVERYTHING.

41:47.347 --> 41:50.416
‐I BEG YOUR PARDON?
‐NO, A PARDON YOU WILL NOT GET.

41:50.416 --> 41:51.552
‐I WARNED YOU.
‐DAVID!

41:51.552 --> 41:53.253
‐HEY! HEY!

41:53.253 --> 41:55.155
WHY CAN'T YOU SEE IT?

41:55.155 --> 41:56.256
AND I GO TO JAIL.

41:56.256 --> 41:57.791
OH, I'LL MAKE SURE OF IT.
